# Stripe Payment Integration - Environment Variables

# ============================================
# STRIPE CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# Get these from: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys

# Stripe Publishable Key (Frontend - Safe to expose)
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=your_publishable_key_here

# Stripe Secret Key (Backend - Keep secret!)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here

# Stripe Webhook Secret (For payment confirmations)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_webhook_secret_here

# ============================================
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR CLIENT
# ============================================
# 1. Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
# 2. Copy the "Publishable key" and paste it in STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
# 3. Copy the "Secret key" and paste it in STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
# 4. For webhooks:
#    - Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks
#    - Add endpoint: https://yourdomain.com/api/stripe/webhook
#    - Select events: payment_intent.succeeded, payment_intent.payment_failed
#    - Copy the "Signing secret" and paste it in STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
